		<title>Aumentando a Privacidade</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://backup/portal/servidores/desktop/aumentando-a-privacidade.html"/>
		<published>2017-10-02T20:52:38-03:00</published>
		<updated>2017-10-02T20:52:38-03:00</updated>
		<id>http://backup/portal/servidores/desktop/aumentando-a-privacidade.html</id>
		<author>
			<name>Ribamar FS</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h2&gt;Protegendo nossa Privacidade&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Vivemos tempos em que nossas informações valem ouro. Elas têm enriquecido muita gente, especialmente quem não nos respeita.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Algumas dicas do instrumento de busca DuckDuckGo para melhorar a privacidade:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/zlaVldA8LGk/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Fiphone-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/W4ynR3fUviY/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Fandroid-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Android&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/NXPHhMtFal8/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Fmac-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Mac&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/wNxUeitkw0k/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Fwindows-10-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Windows 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/nGAwKh9CPrc/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Fwindows-7-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Windows 7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/i8oxyzYSpvs/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Flinux-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Linux&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h2&gt;Protegendo nossa Privacidade&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Vivemos tempos em que nossas informações valem ouro. Elas têm enriquecido muita gente, especialmente quem não nos respeita.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Algumas dicas do instrumento de busca DuckDuckGo para melhorar a privacidade:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://deref-gmx.com/mail/client/zlaVldA8LGk/dereferrer/?redirectUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fspreadprivacy.com%2Fiphone-privacy-tips%2F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;

