		<summary type="html">&lt;h4&gt;Alternativas para o Prompt do Windows&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;O prompt do Windows tem várias limitações (pelo menos até a versão 7):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;- Não fecha com ALT+F4&lt;br /&gt;- Não maximiza a janela&lt;br /&gt;- Não suporta SSH&lt;br /&gt;- Não suporta Git&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;As alternativas abaixo não têm estas limitações &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CMDER&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/cmderdev/cmder/releases/Â&quot;&gt;https://github.com/cmderdev/cmder/releases/ &lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Full e mini &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PowerCMD&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.powercmd.com/&quot;&gt;http://www.powercmd.com/&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ColorConsole&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.softwareok.com/?seite=Freeware/ColorConsole&quot;&gt;http://www.softwareok.com/?seite=Freeware/ColorConsole&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ConEmu&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;https://conemu.github.io/&quot;&gt;https://conemu.github.io/&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Console&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;http://sourceforge.net/projects/console/Â&quot;&gt;http://sourceforge.net/projects/console/ &lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GIT&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-scm.com/&quot;&gt;https://git-scm.com/&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
