		<id>http://backup/portal/servidores/desktop/formatar-pendrive.html</id>
		<author>
			<name>Ribamar FS</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conectarnautilus.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formatar pendrive no Linux&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;sudo fdisk -l (anotar a partição: sdf1)&lt;br /&gt;sudo umount /dev/sdf1 &lt;br /&gt;sudo mkfs.vfat -n 'RIBAFS' -I /dev/sdf1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Alternativa ainda mais completa&lt;/strong&gt; - GParted&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sudo apt-get install gparted&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Obs.: muito cuidado para não formatar a partição do seu HD.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conectarnautilus.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formatar pendrive no Linux&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;sudo fdisk -l (anotar a partição: sdf1)&lt;br /&gt;sudo umount /dev/sdf1 &lt;br /&gt;sudo mkfs.vfat -n 'RIBAFS' -I /dev/sdf1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Alternativa ainda mais completa&lt;/strong&gt; - GParted&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sudo apt-get install gparted&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Obs.: muito cuidado para não formatar a partição do seu HD.&lt;/p&gt;
