		<title>Compactação Multivolume</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://backup/portal/servidores/desktop/compactacao-multivolume.html"/>
		<published>2017-06-24T18:34:48-03:00</published>
		<updated>2017-06-24T18:34:48-03:00</updated>
		<id>http://backup/portal/servidores/desktop/compactacao-multivolume.html</id>
		<author>
			<name>Ribamar FS</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conectarnautilus.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compactar multivolumes no Linux&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Instale os pacots abaixo&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;sudo apt-get -y install unace rar unrar zip unzip p7zip-full p7zip-rar sharutils uudeview mpack arj cabextract file-roller xarchiver&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Estes oferecem suporte via Nautilus/Nemo&lt;br /&gt;.rar ou .7z&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Agora pode compactar multivolume através do modo gráfico com o gerenciador de arquivos Nautilus ou Nemo.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conectarnautilus.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compactar multivolumes no Linux&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Instale os pacots abaixo&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;sudo apt-get -y install unace rar unrar zip unzip p7zip-full p7zip-rar sharutils uudeview mpack arj cabextract file-roller xarchiver&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Estes oferecem suporte via Nautilus/Nemo&lt;br /&gt;.rar ou .7z&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Agora pode compactar multivolume através do modo gráfico com o gerenciador de arquivos Nautilus ou Nemo.&lt;/p&gt;


